# Project Images Folder

Add your project screenshots/images here.

Recommended sizes:
- Width: 1200px minimum
- Height: 800px recommended
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Optimized for web (< 500KB each)

Example structure:
```
projects/
├── ecommerce-app.jpg
├── fitness-tracker.png
├── chat-api.jpg
└── food-delivery.png
```

Then reference them in src/components/Projects.astro:
```javascript
image: "/projects/your-image.jpg"
```
